  "body": "### Description\r\nAs a node operator, when I supply the `--network=` flag, I want Teku to use a different database so that I am not trying to work with invalid data. This could also apply for the default logging location.\r\n\r\nIf users specify their own database path, we assume they know what they are doing. This should ony change the defaults.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* Each variant of the `--network` flag defaults to a different database directory, such as `data_medalla`, `data_altona`, but ony if a specific database location is not otherwise provided.\r\n* Also applies to default logs if the log path is not supplied: `logs_altona`, `logs_medalla`, etc.",
